{"lastModified":1764243079801,"uri":"c::9333109022::vessel::d5ca2330-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Gulet","Sailing"],"description":"Operating Area: Gocek, Fethiye\n\nBella Mare gulet was produced in 2008 and renovated according to new technologies in 2018. It offers you a blue voyage tour with a length of 38 meters. There are 6 double cabins, each with its own shower, WC and air conditioning. You can plan a pleasant and entertaining blue cruise holiday with our Bella Mare boat on any of the Bodrum, Gocek, Marmaris and Fethiye routes. Our Bella Mare boat has separate dining areas on the deck and in the lounge, a fully equipped kitchen, an American bar, and separate living areas for the crew. There are sunbathing areas on the deck where 12 people can easily sunbathe.\n\nThere are canoes, snorkels, masks, fins and simple fishing gear to make the time you spend at sea more enjoyable, and to make the time you spend on the deck more fun, there is a rummy set, backgammon, playing cards, DVD player, music system and air conditioning. Our staff on the boat, with their experience, will be at your service for food preparation, service, daily cleaning and all matters you may need during the blue voyage. Its captain and crew, who are experienced in sailing, will sail when the weather permits and you will be able to experience the pleasure of a sailing blue cruise in the Aegean. To experience an economical and enjoyable blue cruise in Turkish territorial waters, we invite you to a blue voyage by sailing with our Bella Mare gulet.","blueprint":{"name":"BELLA MARE","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5ca2330-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::05b94110-c475-11f0-9344-2b07eb4d16a9/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5ca2330-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::05b8cbe1-c475-11f0-9344-2b07eb4d16a9/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5ca2330-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::05b6d010-c475-11f0-9344-2b07eb4d16a9/{imageVariant}","/med